  card "Feature Engineering\n‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ\nPython" as FE #DCFCE7
  KAFKA -down-> FE
